data.description: Welcome to this charming home located on a quiet cul-de-sac in the highly sought-after Rockwall School District. The lovely and well-maintained home features wood laminate floors, stainless appliances, & floor to ceiling brick fireplace that is sure to become the heart of your home. Enjoy the serenity of your large private master retreat. Included are Smart garage door opener, doorbell, & T-stat. Large backyard perfect for leisure activities. Commuting is made easy with quick access to both Interstate 30 & George Bush Turnpike. Live a life of convenience being close to Rockwall shopping centers & restaurants. In addition, medical services are never too far with the Baylor Scott & White Medical Center nearby. This home isn’t just about its location, it flaunts an impressive layout with large spaces in just the right places, offering a perfect blend of comfort & functionality.
